Invocation Name: how many beans
des: This old English phrase has been passed down through generations of both cultured (and un-cultured) British people. It is high time Alexa also benefitted from this knowledge. Simply ask "Alexa, ask how many beans make five?" No need for an account or special hardware.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
